wgInfoModule.name: wgInfoModule
wgInfoModule.contactinfo: WatchGuard Technologies, Inc. 505 Fifth Avenue South Suite 500 Seattle, WA 98104 United States +1.206.613.6600
wgInfoModule.description: The MIB module describes client information of WatchGuard system.

wgClientMIB.name: wgClientMIB
wgClientMIB.description: This is the base object identifier for DHCP Server, DHCP Client and PPPoE Client

wgClientDHCPServer.name: wgClientDHCPServer
wgClientDHCPServer.description: This is the base object identifier for all DHCP server related information.

wgClientDHCPClient.name: wgClientDHCPClient
wgClientDHCPClient.description: This is the base object identifier for all DHCP client related information.

wgClientPPPoEClient.name: wgClientPPPoEClient
wgClientPPPoEClient.description: This is the base object identifier for all PPPoE client related information.

wgClientDHCPServerEnable.name: wgClientDHCPServerEnable
wgClientDHCPServerEnable.description: Indicates whether if DHCP Server has been enabled.

wgClientDHCPServerStartIpAddress.name: wgClientDHCPServerStartIpAddress
wgClientDHCPServerStartIpAddress.description: The starting IP address of the range of IP addresses leased by the DHCP server.

wgClientDHCPServerEndIpAddress.name: wgClientDHCPServerEndIpAddress
wgClientDHCPServerEndIpAddress.description: The last IP address of the range of IP addresses leased by the DHCP Server.

wgClientDHCPServerLeaseTime.name: wgClientDHCPServerLeaseTime
wgClientDHCPServerLeaseTime.description: The lease time of an address assigned to a DHCP client.

wgClientDHCPServerNum.name: wgClientDHCPServerNum
wgClientDHCPServerNum.description: The total number of entries in the wgClientDHCPServerTable.

wgClientDHCPServerConnTable.name: wgClientDHCPServerConnTable
wgClientDHCPServerConnTable.description: This is the client lease table of the DHCP Server.

wgClientDHCPServerRelayServer.name: wgClientDHCPServerRelayServer
wgClientDHCPServerRelayServer.description: The IP address of remote DHCP server to which DHCP requests should be relayed.

wgClientDHCPServerConnEntry.name: wgClientDHCPServerConnEntry
wgClientDHCPServerConnEntry.description: An entry (conceptual row) containing the leasing information of an assigned address by the DHCP Server.

wgClientDHCPServerConnIPAddr.name: wgClientDHCPServerConnIPAddr
wgClientDHCPServerConnIPAddr.description: The IP address assigned to the client.

wgClientDHCPServerConnMACAddr.name: wgClientDHCPServerConnMACAddr
wgClientDHCPServerConnMACAddr.description: The MAC address of the client.

wgClientDHCPServerConnLeaseTimeStart.name: wgClientDHCPServerConnLeaseTimeStart
wgClientDHCPServerConnLeaseTimeStart.description: The date and time when the lease starts.

wgClientDHCPServerConnLeaseTimeEnd.name: wgClientDHCPServerConnLeaseTimeEnd
wgClientDHCPServerConnLeaseTimeEnd.description: The date and time when the lease ends.

wgClientDHCPClientEnable.name: wgClientDHCPClientEnable
wgClientDHCPClientEnable.description: Indicates whether interface 1 (public) is configured to obtain IP address through DHCP.

wgClientDHCPClientDomainName.name: wgClientDHCPClientDomainName
wgClientDHCPClientDomainName.description: The domain name of the DHCP Client.

wgClientDHCPClientDefaultGateway.name: wgClientDHCPClientDefaultGateway
wgClientDHCPClientDefaultGateway.description: The IP address of the default gateway obtained by the DHCP client.

wgClientDHCPClientDNSOne.name: wgClientDHCPClientDNSOne
wgClientDHCPClientDNSOne.description: The IP address of the primary DNS server obtained by the DHCP client.

wgClientDHCPClientDNSTwo.name: wgClientDHCPClientDNSTwo
wgClientDHCPClientDNSTwo.description: The IP address of the secondary DNS server obtained by the DHCP client.

wgClientPPPoEClientEnable.name: wgClientPPPoEClientEnable
wgClientPPPoEClientEnable.description: Indicates whether the interface 1 (public) is configured to use PPPoE.

wgClientPPPoEClientADSLStatus.name: wgClientPPPoEClientADSLStatus
wgClientPPPoEClientADSLStatus.description: The current ADSL status of the PPPoE Client.

wgClientPPPoEClientLocalIPAddr.name: wgClientPPPoEClientLocalIPAddr
wgClientPPPoEClientLocalIPAddr.description: The IP address obtained by the PPPoE Client.

wgClientPPPoEClientRemoteIPAddr.name: wgClientPPPoEClientRemoteIPAddr
wgClientPPPoEClientRemoteIPAddr.description: The IP Address of the PPP server this PPPoE client connects to.

wgClientPPPoEClientNetMask.name: wgClientPPPoEClientNetMask
wgClientPPPoEClientNetMask.description: The subnet mask of the PPPoE client.

wgClientPPPoEClientDNSOne.name: wgClientPPPoEClientDNSOne
wgClientPPPoEClientDNSOne.description: The IP address of the primary DNS server obtained.

wgClientPPPoEClientDNSTwo.name: wgClientPPPoEClientDNSTwo
wgClientPPPoEClientDNSTwo.description: The IP address of the secondary DNS server obtained.

wgClientPPPoEADSLPeerMACAddr.name: wgClientPPPoEADSLPeerMACAddr
wgClientPPPoEADSLPeerMACAddr.description: The MAC Address of the PPP server this client connects to.

wgClientPPPoEClientConnTime.name: wgClientPPPoEClientConnTime
wgClientPPPoEClientConnTime.description: The connection time of the PPPoE connection.
